description: This is a market on whether the Ohio State Buckeyes will cover a 14 point spread against the Minnesota Golden Gophers in their NCAA football matchup scheduled to take place on September 2, 2021. This market will resolve to “Ohio State” if the Ohio State Buckeyes win by over 14 points, and “Minnesota” if the Minnesota Golden Gophers lose by less than 14 points or win. If the final point margin is exactly 14 points and favors the Buckeyes, the market will resolve 50-50. If the match is postponed to a date on or before October 2, 2021, the same market conditions will apply. If the match is postponed to a date after October 2, 2021, or canceled altogether, the market will resolve 50-50.
